  "title": "BRAND AMBASSADOR",
  "description": "<p>Fresh grad and no experience? No idea what kind of role you want to pursue? Looking for somewhere where you can explore and expand your horizons? <br /><br />Look no further! Join our fun and vibrant team right NOW! We encourage self development and personal growth because we strongly believe that developing personnel is beneficial for both YOU and US. Our team will PUSH you towards your goals. We LOVE positive people and encourage a work hard, play hard environment.</p><p>If you are waiting for your University or ORD to start, this would be a great opportunity for you to build up on your skillsets and to gain an edge over your peers~<br /><br /><strong>What you will do:</strong></p><ul><li>Represent clients’ products and provide the most suitable package to customers based on their needs</li><li>Attend product trainings and upskilling topics</li><li>Monitor brand evolution and competitors’ pricing</li><li>Build customer relationships and organize daily work schedule to call on existing or potential sales outlets</li><li>Provide solutions and ideas to assist company’s growth and expansion</li></ul><p><strong>Who we are looking for:</strong></p><ul><li>Outgoing, people-oriented individuals </li><li>Driven to succeed for YOUR better future</li><li>Analytical and solution driven</li><li>Dare to pick up new challenges</li><li>Being able to learn and adapt quickly, while facing continuously changing demands.</li></ul><p><strong>The Perks:</strong></p><ul><li>1 on 1 coaching and guidance provided </li><li>Progression and advancement based on capability </li><li>Team nights (have fun!)</li><li>Regional exposure and exchange programs </li></ul>",
